{"tid":1855843,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全民公敵 人血饅頭夾公仔機夾口罩","createTime":"2020-02-01T09:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T04:05:44.000Z","uid":79897,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"09c3f1f4d80b8541a87d4b8df193c4de34d79ccb","tid":1855843,"uid":79897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:47:04.000Z","msg":"天水圍新北江有一間叫「一枚大本營」的夾公仔機鋪入面有部機竟然放口罩入去做所謂「生意」，係依家咁危急的時候口罩有多竟然唔係自用又唔係幫人，係放入夾公仔機賺人錢又唔一定夾得出來，最過分係佢本身無所謂保夾（保夾：入錢入到一定金額必定夾出一件貨），係比人踢爆左之後先改成$300一盒口罩，但係會定時消除累積金額，等於唔比人保夾，賺盡一分一毫！個場主/台主仲要貼踢爆佢既手足個大頭出來，自己食人血饅頭，仲要貼人大頭，大家唔係仲縱容依啲人呀！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U84yAKS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU84yAKS.jpg&h=cf3a4b06&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zXM5rRy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzXM5rRy.jpg&h=d499deb4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4tjwif.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4tjwif.jpg&h=00a45672&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d47f54b2aa4588c1037e6410b9182b820e1e901","tid":1855843,"uid":149844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:50:10.000Z","msg":"急到無口罩用仲玩鳩人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f0edc5ea60acebf113d9a28c295a1c6e71e5f1","tid":1855843,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:50:20.000Z","msg":"邊度仲有，想夾"},{"pid":"7559180aef6bfe5121ceacb1853788d1ca8d6744","tid":1855843,"uid":309664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:16:37.000Z","msg":"toreba都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50fb75bd6a0d7158cd27468ee82c49ca0d0506a","tid":1855843,"uid":79897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80f0edc5ea60acebf113d9a28c295a1c6e71e5f1","tid":1855843,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T09:50:20.000Z","msg":"邊度仲有，想夾"},"